<item>
            <title>[AMQ-7497] RAR xaResource needs to support reconnect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-7497</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Inbound MDBs supported by endpoint workers in the RAR support reconnect and failover with maxReconnects=0. In this way the failover transport can support the use of multiple brokers.&lt;br/&gt;
The failover url with no reconnects will leave the resource adapter single xaResource connection in an invalid state after disconnect and will cause periodic recovery to fail.&lt;br/&gt;
The single RA wide xaResource should reconnect any failed connection on subsequent usage.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
